text: Renford Pinnock (26 September 1937 - 1 November 2019) was a Jamaican cricketer. He played 44 first-class matches for Jamaica between 1963 and 1975. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1937 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Jamaican cricketers Category:Jamaica cricketers Category:People from Saint Catherine Parish
